commentable_entity.title: Amber Heard deserves punishment for her wrongful actions
commentable_entity.description: As you see and are following, Amber Heard has accused Johnny Depp of abuse that he never did. She, Amber was the abuser. Just because she is a woman, doesn’t mean that she wasn’t the abuser. He nor anyone deserves to go through what he has gone through with her. With that being said, she deserves to have consequences for her actions and the mental damage she has done to Johnny. Please sign this petition if you agree that she needs to be punished for what she did and the nasty person that she is.
